* '''Playing Time:''' 
* '''Setting:''' [[Moonsea]]

document_data.DDEX1-04 - Dues for the Dead:
{{main|Dues for the Dead}}

{{Quote|''For years, the Most Solemn [[Order of the Silent Shroud]] has tended the dead at [[Valhingen Graveyard]], providing them a peaceful eternal rest. Now, that rest has been disturbed by a necromancer seeking out a key to re-activate the [[Pool of Radiance]].''|}}

