document_data.DDEX1-05 - The Courting of Fire:
{{main|The Courting of Fire}}

{{Quote|''An exiled cultist and his [[kobold]] minions are spotted searching for long-forgotten ruins in the [[Dragonspire Mountains]]. Rumors say he looks for a precious gift to give a fearsome dragon that dwells there. What he hopes to attain wiht his gift is unknowen, but can't be good for the citizens of [[Phlan]].''|}}

