document_data.DDEX1-11 - Dark Pyramid of Sorcerer's Is:
{{main|Dark Pyramid of Sorcerer's Isle}}

{{Quote|''Long unoccupied, the pyramid on [[Sorcerer’s Isle]] now flows with strange magical energy, warping creatures and the landscape around it. The [[Cult of the Dragon]] and [[Red Wizards of Thay]] have taken notice, and it’s up to you to keep whatever power dwells there out of their hands.''|}}

