document_data.DDEX1-12 - Raiders of the Twilight Marsh:
{{main|Raiders of the Twilight Marsh}}

{{Quote|''A [[black dragon]]'s treasure horde has been located in the [[Twilight Marsh]], and within it are secrets that hold interest to the factions. With the dragon marauding over the countryside, the horde is left unguarded. Now is the time to plunder its lair!''|}}

