document_data.DDEX1-14 - Escape from Phlan:
{{main|Escape from Phlan}}

{{Quote|''Three important citizens of [[Phlan]], who stand against the tyrannical dragon that rules, seek to escape and find refuge across the [[Moonsea]]. Can you extricate those that are vital to the factions before it’s too late?''|}}

